title: 215: DJ's Top 25 Rookies
itunes:title: 215: DJ's Top 25 Rookies
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks get you ready for this weekend's action by breaking down the Cowboys and Packers match up, analyzing how the college game influences the NFL, and predicting how Mitchell Trubisky will fare in his first start. DJ also reveals his Top 25 rookies list at the quarter poll of the season. The guys also pick the biggest upcoming games in college football.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
